title: Jeremy Corbyn repeatedly refuses to confirm he will kneel before the Queen
text: Jeremy Corbyn Jeremy Corbyn repeatedly refuses to confirm he will kneel before the Queen The Labour leader refused to answer the question three times and instead claimed he does not know 'what the ceremony involves' Jeremy Corbyn has refused to confirm he will kneel before the Queen Photo: Bloomberg Kate McCann and Auslan Cramb 6:51PM BST 09 Oct 2015
